uency in-plane phonon mode decreases in frequency for $T < T_N$,\nsuggesting the possibility of spin-phonon coupling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jul 2013 17:53:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Feb 2014 15:52:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-21"}
