introduction of a small Majorana mass term breaks the\n$R$-symmetry, splitting the Dirac neutralino into a pair of nearly degenerate\nMajorana states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jul 2013 20:00:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Nov 2013 15:33:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-05"}
